    "body": "I return having sifted through some backlog.\r\n\r\nFollowing #25236, fix #24032 by stripping the local `file:` prefix before `gf` and `<cfile>` path resolution. Other URL handling is not changed.",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-14T22:08:09Z",
